reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Need Better Directions
reviews.reviewText: The directions were too vague and needed to have step by step on what to do. There wasn't clear instructions how to get the computer hooked up and where to plug the main mesh into. A step by step with illustrations would be very helpful. Sorta like hooking this up for Dummys.We will see how it performs with the devices we have. Had a lot less loading on the TV and was hoping that the speed was going to fix that.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works better than I could have expected!
reviews.reviewText: I was a bit skeptical trying an off brand mesh network but on the recommendation from a close friend, I decided to give this a try and I am blown away. Very simple to setup and no drop in speeds where I previously had drops using my google wifi. Not sure how they were able to out perform Google on what I'm sure is a much smaller budget, but they have pulled it off. I can't recommend this mesh setup enough.
